00:39:19,361 --> 00:39:22,261
<font color="yellow">I told you to let go.</font>

294
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:26,861
<font color="yellow">Let go of him.</font>

295
00:39:29,661 --> 00:39:33,361
<font color="yellow">Let go of him, okay? Now.</font>

