00:42:01,060 --> 00:42:19,761
<font color="yellow">Abra...cadabra.
Abra...cadabra.</font>

303
00:42:22,460 --> 00:42:34,761
<font color="yellow">Abra...cadabra.
Abra...cadabra.</font>

