353
00:56:27,761 --> 00:56:33,261
<font color="yellow">If Hong Joo finds out about that,
Mr. Heo will be in danger.</font>

354
00:56:33,861 --> 00:56:35,861
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

355
00:56:36,861 --> 00:56:45,560
<font color="yellow">Yoh Gwang. If I become
evil once more, kill me.</font>

356
00:56:49,361 --> 00:56:53,261
<font color="yellow">I can't do that.
I won't!</font>

357
00:56:57,060 --> 00:57:04,261
<font color="yellow">I'm begging you. If I'm a danger
to Yeon Hui, you must not hesitate</font>

358
00:57:04,261 --> 00:57:06,661
<font color="yellow">and save Yeon Hui.</font>

359
00:57:11,060 --> 00:57:19,861
<font color="yellow">Please kill me before Poong Yeon
and Yeon Hui see me in my evil state.</font>

360
00:59:16,960 --> 00:59:19,361
<font color="yellow">What do you want?</font>

361
00:59:26,861 --> 00:59:30,560
<font color="yellow">Am I crazy to want an apology from you?</font>

362
00:59:30,560 --> 00:59:33,960
<font color="yellow">I mean, it really did hurt
